# SSH Configuration
# =================
# This file is installed by dotfiles. Customise it for your hosts.
# See .ssh/config.example for more detailed examples.

# GitHub
Host github.com
  AddKeysToAgent yes
  UseKeychain yes                    # macOS only, remove on Linux
  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519    # Update with your key path

# Add your own hosts below:
# -------------------------
# Host example
#     User your_username
#     HostName example.com
